<section id="about" class="section about-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">About Us</h2>
    <div class="about-content">
      <div class="about-image">
        <img src="https://retail-merchandiser.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/8/2024/02/Pick-up-and-delivery-services-image.jpeg" alt="Super Speed Express team" />
      </div>
      <div class="about-text">
        <p>Founded in 2023, Super Speed Express is driven by a mission to provide courier and delivery services that go beyond logistics. Our goal is not only to deliver efficiently but to build lasting relationships with our clients through trust, technology, and innovation.</p>
        
        <div class="vision-mission">
          <div class="vm-item">
            <h3>Vision</h3>
            <p>"To be the foremost provider of cutting-edge and reliable courier services, consistently exceeding client expectations."</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="vm-item">
            <h3>Mission</h3>
            <p>"To deliver excellence in every parcel and interaction through innovation, commitment, and a customer-centric approach."</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-section {
    background-color: var(--color-light-gray);
  }
  
  .about-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  
  .about-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }
  
  .about-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  
  .about-text p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  
  .vision-mission {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }
  
  .vm-item {
    background-color: var(--color-white);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .vm-item:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }
  
  .vm-item h3 {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .vm-item p {
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .about-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
    
    .vision-mission {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .about-content {
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .vm-item {
      text-align: left;
    }
  }
</style>